<item>
            <title>[AMQ-3022] ActiveMQ does not support suspend/resume of transactions </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-3022</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A user of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://btm.codehaus.org/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bitronix transaction manager&lt;/a&gt; had trouble with ActiveMQ and its ability to suspend/resume transactions. See the &lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/BTM-87&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bitronix issue&lt;/a&gt; for more information. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
